{"tid":2283934,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪連登仔嘅職業：貓義工","createTime":"2020-11-13T02:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T09:13:43.000Z","uid":259980,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9ab3a3103b9fe812901581fb746f74088b6cb03a","tid":2283934,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:51:08.000Z","msg":"喺連登唔可以叫人領養<br />\n唔可以屌人買貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33220af859b9861a4a570dea1dcee7991aa518e0","tid":2283934,"uid":196924,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"貓義工嘅問題唔係叫人領養代替購買<br />\n啱啱相反<br />\n佢地會叫人領養，又要家訪又乜乜柒柒<br />\n好心領養仲要俾佢地當係賊咁查家宅<br />\n最撚仆街係佢地套邏輯<br />\n未養過，佢地會質疑你，唔係咁想俾你領養<br />\n咁冇得領養就諗住去買啦，又係會俾佢地屌<br />\n同啲招聘廣告fg兩年工作經驗一鳩樣"},{"pid":"63686eba4fd25e078ebd2d77e433e08a933a0458","tid":2283934,"uid":57554,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:20:17.000Z","msg":"自己係街執算"},{"pid":"6f150f978c5c235f318203870567fd28d1278ff9","tid":2283934,"uid":133763,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"屌連登仔師<br />\n要養貓都係搵朋友好過啦"},{"pid":"74f35b079dd7cc9a72105a2edfb4bae35e9c6d37","tid":2283934,"uid":32588,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"仲有貓義工會偷貓<br />\n同埋雙重標準<br />\n對領養者要求高得不合理<br />\n但自己養貓個竇差到就近乎虐畜"},{"pid":"4c7c9ed6c719a9acaf7be16646c4110fb7f0ff84","tid":2283934,"uid":8439,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:25:33.000Z","msg":"去領養問你經濟情況<br />\n無錢:養唔起貓貓 有咩事睇醫生都無錢<br />\n有錢:掛住做野 唔會有時間俾到貓貓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf33211d7287485c589f6029ce2ef39bd3255e82","tid":2283934,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:26:48.000Z","msg":"你去做貓義工囉"},{